                "invention-title": [
                    "Polymer composition, epoxy resin composition, curing agent for epoxy resin, and rapid-curing adhesive",
                    "聚合物组合物、环氧树脂组合物、环氧树脂用固化剂及快速固化型粘接剂"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The purpose of the present invention is to provide: a polymer composition which can be used as a curing agent for an epoxy resin, said curing agent having a high curing speed even in a low-temperature environment, a low viscosity, and good stability and adhesiveness; and an epoxy resin composition. This polymer composition contains a thiol group-containing polyether polymer that has a polyether moiety represented by chemical formula (1) in the main chain and a structural unit represented by formula (2) at the terminal, the thiol group content of the thiol group-containing polyether polymer being 8 mass% or more, and the content of the thiol group-containing polyether polymer being 100 mass% or more. The polymer composition further comprises a cationic surfactant. R1 [-(R2O) n] m-... formula (1) wherein R1 is a residue obtained by removing a hydrogen atom from a polyamine or polyol having 10 or less carbon atoms, R2 is an alkylene group having 2-6 carbon atoms, n is 1-200, and m is 2-8. Formula (2):-CH2CH (OH) CH2-SH."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明的目的在于提供聚合物组合物及环氧树脂组合物，该聚合物组合物可以作为即使在低温环境下固化速度也快、且为低粘度并具有良好的稳定性和粘接性的环氧树脂的固化剂使用。本发明的聚合物组合物包含具有硫醇基的聚醚聚合物，所述具有硫醇基的聚醚聚合物在主链中具有下述化学式(1)表示的聚醚部分、且在末端具有下述式(2)表示的结构单元，所述具有硫醇基的聚醚聚合物的硫醇基含量为8质量％以上，所述聚合物组合物还包含阳离子表面活性剂。R1[‑(R2O)n]m‑…式(1)其中，R1是从碳原子数为10以下的多元胺或多元醇中除去氢原子后的残基，R2是碳原子数为2～6的亚烷基，n为1～200，m为2～8。‑CH2CH(OH)CH2‑SH…式(2)。"
                }
            ]
